         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Director of the Botanic Gardens ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I am instructed by the Committee of the Victorian Gardeners' Mutual Improvement Society to request that you will contribute towards the exhibition to be held...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">60.10.00</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas McMillan</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MS 12521 Victorian Horticultural Society records, box 3401, p. 63, La Trobe Australian Manuscripts Collection, State Library of Victoria, Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS written into minutes of the meeting of the Victorian Gardeners' Mutual Improvement Society held on 29 October 1860. M<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>agreed<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>T. McMillan, November 1860 (in this edition as 60-11-00).</p>
               </note>Director of the Botanic Gardens</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am instructed by the Committee of the Victorian Gardeners' Mutual Improvement Society to request that you will contribute towards the exhibition to be held in connection with the Society as per enclosed schedule<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Schedule not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on the 22d and 23d of Novr by sending plants &amp;c in the same liberal way which you have hitherto done to the Horticultural Society.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The show was held at the Central Market; M contributed a 'collection of emperor Stocks' (<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Victorian farmers journal and gardeners chronicle</seg>, 24 November 1860, p. 18).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The committee ventures to hope that you will the more readily accord your support on this occasion as the G. M. I. Soc is not backed up by Government grants of money and large annual subscriptions but is getting up this its first show at its own cost and not with any view to rival the Horti Soc<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Horticultural Society of Victoria.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>but from a sincere desire to promote Horticulture and to encourage a taste for Horticultural pursuits on the part of the working classes who are from the highly fashionable character which the shows of the Horti Soc. has assumed as it were excluded from enjoying the benefits and recreation to be derived at Exhibitions of Horticultural produce</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I am Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obt Servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>T. McMillan</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hon Sec</p>
         </div>
